sentences.english: Single gray if better with automatic clearance.
sentences.chinese: 單機如果能帶自動清灰灰更好。

sentences.english: If it is an umbrella, memory is the most clear coagulation red umbrella.
sentences.chinese: 倘若是打傘，記憶最深的是清凝的紅傘。

sentences.english: Masa, " he said, having cleared his throat several times."
sentences.chinese: “瑪莎，”他清了幾個嗓子後說道。

sentences.english: Lift your voice so that everyone can hear you with ease.
sentences.chinese: 把嗓門提高，讓大家都能毫不費力地聽清你的話。

sentences.english: Shell has still not been able to say why the leak occurred in the first place.
sentences.chinese: 殼牌仍未能說清爲何泄漏在第一處發生。

sentences.english: It's not easy to count the number of vibrations of shale shaker.
sentences.chinese: 要數清震動篩的振盪數是不容易的。

sentences.english: This wine goes great with herb roasted chicken or seared snapper with capers.
sentences.chinese: 這款酒搭配香草烤雞或清烤魚最佳。

sentences.english: ObjectiveTo observe the effects of Xuezhiqing Capsule on the lipid metabolism in the hyperlipidemia rats.
sentences.chinese: 目的觀察血脂清膠囊對高脂大鼠脂質代謝的影響。

sentences.english: The magnificent Ming and Qing palaces' pillars are red and the tiles are yellow.
sentences.chinese: 這座宏偉的明，清時代的宮殿是紅柱黃瓦。

sentences.english: Under water that was clear as glass the pool was carpeted with green sponge.
sentences.chinese: 在清明如鏡的水底鋪着一層碧綠的海綿。

sentences.english: Wada, a Japanese scholar pointed out this, but he did not do a careful textual research on it.
sentences.chinese: 日本學者和田清曾指出了這一點，但未細考。

sentences.english: The effects of repeated chlorothalonil treatments on soil enzyme activities were similar to those on soil microbes.
sentences.chinese: 百菌清反覆處理對土壤酶的影響也呈類似趨勢。

sentences.english: Objective To study the water extracting technical condition of Juhuang Shangqing Buccal Tablet.
sentences.chinese: 目的優選菊黃上清含片的水煎煮提取工藝條件。

sentences.english: By just picking up litter and refraining from littering we are doing meritorious deeds.
sentences.chinese: 能不亂丟垃圾，隨時清撿垃圾，都是做的功德。

sentences.english: The new "Ming" will just react to the "Qing" policies.
sentences.chinese: 新“明”會是“清”的政策反動。

sentences.english: Meadows still smell of hay and the sweetness of cut grass.
sentences.chinese: 草場上披髮着新草垛及新刈綠草的清噴香。
